{
  "text": "Y. enterocolitica 8081 was grown in TSB broth with 20 mM MgCl 2, washed and diluted in sterile PBS supplemented with 10% iron dextran solution and IP challenged (10 8 CFU/mice) [CITATION_1] . Mortality and morbidity were recorded for 24 days post challenge. On 2, 7, 14, and 21 days of challenge, one mouse from each group was injected with 200 \u03bcl of 0.5% xylazine and 0.2% ketamine mixture (200:1) and humanely killed to censor the health status and Colony Forming Unit (CFU) count in spleen and liver [CITATION_2] . The survival percentage in each group of challenged mice was calculated by using Kaplan Meier method.",
